race.comment: STARLIGHT SNOWY (6) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.69 beating RAPIDO NINJA. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can make it two on the bounce. RAPIDO NINJA (4) could finish only among the minors last time (30.04) at this track bringing a three run winning streak to an end. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. BANGOR TIGER (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (28.17) in a Grade 5 at Mandurah. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. JUST A NUISANCE (2) missed the frame latest (30.44) when fifth over 520m at this track in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw.
